BRIEF-Zhejiang New Jialian Electronics gets regulatory approval for assets acquisition Sept 8 
Sept 8 Zhejiang New Jialian Electronics Co Ltd 
* Says gets securities regulator's approval for assets acquisition, shares to resume trading on Sept 9
